{"tid":955211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國有法院裁定北韓要就瓦姆比爾的死付其家人5億美元","createTime":"2018-12-25T08:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T08:35:34.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"32d65eb727002f7dae57b5b80af284a9b7368a69","tid":955211,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"美國有法院裁定北韓要就瓦姆比爾的死付其家人5億美元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434907-20181225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434907-20181225.htm&d=%2Bx%2FO5aMVOz%2Fb6Hk2i1FBc8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b13e72b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434907-20181225.htm&h=27d16acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434907-20181225.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國華盛頓哥倫比亞特區一個法院裁定，北韓當局要就美國大學生瓦姆比爾的死，向入稟索償的瓦姆比爾家人，支付超過5億美元。<br />\n<br />\n法官指出，瓦姆比爾遭受北韓的殘酷對待，北韓將瓦姆比爾視為抵押品，用來與美國交易。<br />\n<br />\n瓦姆比爾早年前往北韓，被指在酒店竊取北韓宣傳海報，判勞教15年，服刑一年半後，在去年獲釋，送返美國時陷於昏迷，留醫數日後死亡。"},{"pid":"2f65f218ffe5602fc8e6340966b87ef2beb932c9","tid":955211,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c6f468bfcfb9be2e6d389fccb1fd59c1ceee7e7","tid":955211,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f65f218ffe5602fc8e6340966b87ef2beb932c9","tid":955211,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"充公北韓啲資產？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}